          h3 We'd love to hear from you !
          p Write to us, we'd love to hear from you ! If you are interested in our services, get a 
            a(href="#") consultation call
          form(action='example@example' method='POST').contact-main__content-form
            label
              span Full Name*
              input(type="text" required='')
              span.invalid-title Please fill this field
            label
              span Email address*
              input(type="email" required='')
              span.invalid-title Please fill this field
            label.text-label    
              span Your Message    
              textarea(rows='1' cols='1')
            label.checkbox-label.terms(for='1')
              input#1.checkbox(type='checkbox' required='' checked)
              span.checkmark
              span.text
                | I want to get Area99 annual report on industry competiveness.
              button Send
